<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Reset your TideTogether password</h2>
    <p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your TideTogether account. Click the button below to choose a new password.</p>
    <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
      <a href="<%= @reset_url %>"
         style="background:#F38046; color:#fff; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;">
        Reset Password
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>This link expires in <strong>2 hours</strong>. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password will not change.</p>
    <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break:break-all; font-size:0.85rem; color:#555;"><%= @reset_url %></p>
    <hr style="margin-top:32px; border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee;">
    <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#888;">TideTogether &mdash; Northwestern University Study Assistant</p>
  </body>
</html>
